<div class="headban gheadban">            
    <div class="middle_wrap">
        <h1>공지사항</h1>
        <ul class="mnavi">
            <li><a href="#">공지사항</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">행사안내</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">언론보도</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">입점문의</a></li>
        </ul>
    </div>       
</div>    
</header>
<main>
    <div class="wrap1200 content_box">
        <div id="content">
            <div class="subpg_title_wrap">
                <h2 class="subpg_title">공지사항</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="write_t_wrap">
                <a href="notice">목록</a>
            </div> 
            <div class="answer">
                <h3>문의하시기 전 확인해 주세요.</h3>
            </div>
            <div>
                <ul class="imp_notice">
                    <li>· 고객님의 소중한 의견을 빠르고 정확하게 해결하기 위해 최선을 다하겠습니다.</li>
                    <li>· 예약한 상품의 취소는 카톡이나 Q&A를 통해 문의해 주세요.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <% if(typeof errs !== 'undefined'){ %>
                <%errs.forEach(()=>{%>
                    <h3><%=err.param%> : <%=err.msg%></h3>
                <%})%>
            <%}%>
            <div class="write_table">
                <form method="POST" action="/updateMemo">
                    <input type="hidden" name="id" value="<%=row.id%>">
                    <table border="1" id="w_table">
                        <colgroup>
                            <col style="width: 18%;">
                        </colgroup>
                        <tbody>
                              <tr>
                                  <th>
                                      <span class="impt">이름</span>
                                  </th>
                                  <td>
                                      <div class="form_name">
                                          <input type="text" name="writer" class="input_p name_im" style="width: 30%;" value="<%=row.writer%>">
                                      </div>
                                  </td>
                              </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th>
                                    <span class="impt">제목</span>
                                </th>
                                <td>
                                    <div class="form_title">
                                       <input type="text" name="title" class="input_title" style="width: 100%;" value="<%=row.title%>">
                                    </div>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th>
                                    <span class="impt">내용</span>
                                </th>
                                <td>
                                    <div class="form_text">
                                        <textarea name="content" style="width: 100%;"><%=row.content%></textarea>
                                    </div>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                          </tbody>
                    </table>
                    <input type="submit" value="submit">
                    <input type="button" value="back" onclick="javascript:location.href ='notice'">
                </form>               
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>

